Output docs/assets/demo.gif
Set Theme "Catppuccin Latte"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 800
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set BorderRadius 10

Hide
Type "export AGENTS_DRY_RUN=true"
Enter
Type "./bin/swarm"
Enter
Sleep 2s
Show

Type "Build and test this repository"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 25s

Type "Now deploy it to production"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 15s
